Board entity
The Board and Pieces entities form an aggregate of entities, with the Board as the aggregate root.
A Piece can only have a position if the board allows it. The board MUST control the state, to apply it's rules. Examples:
Only one piece per position.
The plays should be validated against all pieces in the board, to check for global conditions, suck as "cant leave your own king in check".
